column2: SELECT TOP #   x.objID AS xObjID,pz.objID AS pzObjID, p.objID AS pObjID, s.specObjID, s.bestObjID   p.flag_u, p.flag_g, p.flag_r, p.flag_i, p.flag_z FROM MyDB.FIRST_RADec_Half AS f   CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq(f.ra, f.dec, #) AS x   JOIN PhotoObjAll p ON x.objID = p.objID   JOIN SpecObjAll s ON p.objID = s.bestObjID   JOIN Photoz pz ON x.objID = pz.objID where (flags & @bad_flags) = # and nChild=#
